{"tid":984583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢收「家姐」短訊墮騙局　被呃43萬元點數卡","createTime":"2019-01-17T02:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T10:22:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"36cde98e2747741a1774078619dc2f34094580d7","tid":984583,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117010925712-0117_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190117093044\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117010925712-0117_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190117093044&h=9d554c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有人墮入電騙陷阱！一名姓朱（48歲）男子，報稱早前接獲「家姐」傳來的手機短訊，要求弟弟代購點數卡，他不虞有詐，按指示先後多次購買總值43萬港元的點數卡，隨後亦全數將其轉戶，及後他認為有可疑，向家姐求證後確認受騙。昨日（16日）傍晚6時許，他在屯門青山公路黃金海岸住所報警求助。警員初步調查後，列為以欺騙手段取得財產案，由屯門警區列事調查隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117010925712-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117010925712-0117_00822_001.html&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d8688803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117010925712-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"94cf0001a53e5efae8e1a429107c4e35547d969d","tid":984583,"uid":54359,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"關家姐事？"},{"pid":"974b7f573ec69d3b22be6a4d218b3ede16b39fae","tid":984583,"uid":34243,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"有咩原因要幫家姐買43萬野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5912524dcbe7a7f40648c48cbd1051684fbb8e2d","tid":984583,"uid":45788,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:27:01.000Z","msg":"及後他認為有可疑，向家姐求證後確認受騙。<br />\n<br />\n唔識先求證再入點咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif